    <item>
      <title>#whoami</title>
      <link>https://www.thephantomninja.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Dec 2015 20:30:12 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.thephantomninja.com/about/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;Hi. The Phantom Ninja blog is dedicated to discussing my passions. Namely, technology and personal finance. I specifically love (useful) mobile applications, security and living debt free.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;why-would-you-want-my-opinion&#34;&gt;Why would you want my opinion?&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s a good question, and I hope you find the answer to that as you delve into the content here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;what-s-my-story&#34;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s my story?&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Much of my story will be told amongst my posts here. For background, however, some highlights are below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;li&gt; 15 years in the technology industry - including enterprise IT, audio/video, lighting and consumer tech&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;li&gt; paid off over $40,000 in personal/consumer debt&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
